{"title":"阳光","date":"2020-05-31T05:59:39.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 31, 2020","L":"05/31/2020","MM-DD":"05-31"},"author":"WardZhou","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/summer-2391348_640.jpg","link":"2020/05/31/Sunshine","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.496Z","content":"<p>你一定是受阿波罗眷顾的孩子<br>\n因为有你在的地方<br>\n即便是夜晚<br>\n也有一片明媚的阳光<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p>星星点点地<br>\n只要有种子在心中落下<br>\n唦——唦——<br>\n在星空的闪耀下<br>\n就这样踮着脚<br>\n生长起希望</p>\n<p>等白昼来临<br>\n已是绿荫茂茂</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>谨以此诗献给s莎</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"玫瑰 Just Rose","link":"2020/06/01/RosePapercutting"},"next":{"title":"无梦的夜 Dreamless Night","link":"2020/05/25/DreamlessNight"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/05/31/Sunshine/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"WardZhou","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"}}